overview: On November 12th Nick Gage Invitational 7 is live and exclusively on FITE+ straight from Summit Park District, IL. The first match is already announced and it's the First Round Death Match where Big Joe takes on John Wayne Murdoch.  The other three opening round matches are:  Toshiyuki Sakuda vs Ciclope Miedo Extremo vs Cole Radrick Alex Colon vs Sawyer Wreck vs Hunter Freeman
title: GCW Nick Gage Invitational 7
